    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The technique of painting with pigments in a water-soluble binder and thinned with water, usually on paper. The concept includes gouache painting as it is a form of gum-bound water soluble paint.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
